'''Draethos''' was the official language of [[Draethos (planet)|Draethos]], used by its native [[Species/Legends|species]], the [[Draethos/Legends|Draethos]]. It was described as a flurry of cacophonous sighs and clicks.<ref name="Ultimate Alien Anthology" />

